text: Ladawan Mulasartsatorn (born 18 March 1970) is a Thai badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Thai female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Thailand Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Badminton players at the 1986 Asian Games Category:Badminton players at the 1990 Asian Games
